# Project Structure

This is a full-stack web application with the following main components:

- `backend/` - Node.js backend with Prisma ORM for database operations
  - `prisma/` - Database schema definition
  - `routes/` - API endpoints
  - `uploads/` - Storage for documents
  - `generated/` - Auto-generated code files

- `src/` - Frontend React application
  - `app/` - Next.js app router components
  - `components/` - Reusable UI components
  - `pages/` - Page components and routes
  - `api/` - API client for backend communication
  - `services/` - Business logic services
  - `types/` - TypeScript type definitions
  - `hooks/` - Custom React hooks
  - `lib/` - Utility functions and helpers

- `public/` - Static assets
- `shared/` - Code shared between frontend and backend

## Key Areas

- User management (employees, trainers)
- Course management 
- Company management
- Schedule and attendance tracking
- Document generation (attestati/certificates)
